_CURSECHANCE_FULL:"诅咒概率",STAT_CURSECHANCE_LABEL:"CRS",STAT_CURSECHANCE_STACKDESC:"When attacking, targets with Curse stacks take recoil damage equal to 1% of the originator's ATK per stack.",STAT_DECAY_IMMUNE_HINT:"不受衰变系数影响",STAT_DODGE_DESC:"完全躲开攻击的概率，从而免受伤害和状态影响。受攻击者命中属性的克制。",STAT_DODGE_FULL:"闪避概率",STAT_DODGE_LABEL:"闪避",STAT_ELECTROCUTECHANCE_DESC:"Chance to apply Electrocute. Targets take random additional damage (0 to 1% of incoming damage per stack) when hit. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_ELECTROCUTECHANCE_FULL:"电击概率",STAT_ELECTROCUTECHANCE_LABEL:"ELC",STAT_ELECTROCUTECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Targets take random additional damage (0 to 1% of incoming damage per stack) when hit.",STAT_ENERGYWAVECHANCE_DESC:"Chance to gain Energy Wave stacks on attack. Every second, 10% of stacks (min 1) are consumed to deal damage to the enemy equal to [Consumed Stacks] × [Attack]. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_ENERGYWAVECHANCE_FULL:"能量波概率",STAT_ENERGYWAVECHANCE_LABEL:"EWC",STAT_ENERGYWAVECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Every second, 10% of stacks (min 1) are consumed to deal damage to the enemy equal to [Consumed Stacks] × [Attack].",STAT_EXACERBATECHANCE_DESC:"Chance when attacking to randomly select one debuff currently affecting the target and add an extra stack of it. Values over 100% can add multiple stacks.",STAT_EXACERBATECHANCE_FULL:"恶化概率",STAT_EXACERBATECHANCE_LABEL:"EXA",STAT_EXECUTE_DESC:"当目标生命值低于 30% 时造成的百分比额外伤害。",STAT_EXECUTE_FULL:"斩杀伤害",STAT_EXECUTE_LABEL:"斩杀",STAT_FRAILTYCHANCE_DESC:"施加虚弱状态的概率（每层增加 1% 受到的伤害）。",STAT_FRAILTYCHANCE_FULL:"虚弱概率",STAT_FRAILTYCHANCE_LABEL:"虚弱",STAT_FRAILTYCHANCE_STACKDESC:"Each stack increases final damage taken by 1%.",STAT_FREEZECHANCE_DESC:"完全停止对手行动。",STAT_FREEZECHANCE_FULL:"冻结概率",STAT_FREEZECHANCE_LABEL:"冻结",STAT_FREEZECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Each stack reduces Health Regen by 1%. Above 100 stacks, Regen becomes damage. If no Regen exists, deals 1 damage per stack/sec instead.",STAT_GLANCINGBLOW_DESC:"将受到的暴击降级为正常命中的概率。",STAT_GLANCINGBLOW_FULL:"擦伤概率",STAT_GLANCINGBLOW_LABEL:"擦伤",STAT_GOLDENLUCKCHANCE_DESC:"Chance when landing a critical hit to multiply the critical damage by the Golden Luck Crit Damage multiplier.",STAT_GOLDENLUCKCHANCE_FULL:"金色幸运概率",STAT_GOLDENLUCKCHANCE_LABEL:"GLC",STAT_GOLDENLUCKDAMAGE_DESC:"Additional multiplier applied to critical hits that trigger Golden Luck. Multiplies with your Critical Damage modifier. Base is 1.5×.",STAT_GOLDENLUCKDAMAGE_FULL:"金色幸运伤害",STAT_GOLDENLUCKDAMAGE_LABEL:"GLD",STAT_HASTECHANCE_DESC:"Chance to gain Haste on attack. Each stack increases attack speed by 0.1% (making SPD delay shorter). Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_HASTECHANCE_FULL:"急速概率",STAT_HASTECHANCE_LABEL:"HST",STAT_HASTECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Each stack increases attack speed by 0.1%.",STAT_HINDERCHANCE_DESC:"Chance to apply Hinder. Each stack provides a 0.1% chance (capped at 1000 stacks or 100%) for the target's attack to fail. Stacks are reduced by half upon trigger. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_HINDERCHANCE_FULL:"Hinder Chance",STAT_HINDERCHANCE_LABEL:"HIN",STAT_HINDERCHANCE_STACKDESC:"Each stack provides a 0.1% chance (capped at 100%) for the target's attack to fail. Stacks are reduced by half upon trigger.",STAT_HOTPOTATOCHANCE_DESC:"Chance to apply Hot Potato to enemy. When the holder attacks, rolls for: 50% gain 1, 10% gain 5, 5% gain 10, 10% double, 3% triple, 2% quadruple, 15% explode (damage = stacks to holder, clear stacks), 5% pass all stacks to opponent. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_HOTPOTATOCHANCE_FULL:"烫手山芋概率",STAT_HOTPOTATOCHANCE_LABEL:"HOT",STAT_HOTPOTATOCHANCE_STACKDESC:"When the holder attacks, rolls for: 50% gain 1, 10% gain 5, 5% gain 10, 10% double, 3% triple, 2% quadruple, 15% explode (damage = stacks), 5% pass stacks to opponent.",STAT_HYPNOTIZECHANCE_DESC:"施加催眠状态的概率（每层 0.1% 概率攻击自身）。",STAT_HYPNOTIZECHANCE_FULL:"催眠概率",STAT_HYPNOTIZECHANCE_LABEL:"催眠",STAT_HYPNOTIZECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Targets have a 0.1% chance per stack to attack themselves instead (capped at 100%). Stacks clear upon trigger.",STAT_IMMUNITIES_DESC:"Passive resistance to specific status effects and special combat mechanics. Immune units cannot be affected by the listed stats.",STAT_IMMUNITIES_FULL:"Immunities",STAT_IMMUNITIES_HEADER:"Immunities",STAT_IMMUNITIES_LABEL:"IMM",STAT_INSPIRATIONCHANCE_DESC:"Percent chance to gain a stack of Inspiration every second in combat. Each stack increases damage dealt by 1%. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per second.",STAT_INSPIRATIONCHANCE_FULL:"Inspiration Chance",STAT_INSPIRATIONCHANCE_LABEL:"INS",STAT_INSPIRATIONCHANCE_STACKDESC:"Each stack increases damage dealt by 1%.",STAT_IRRADIATECHANCE_DESC:"Chance to apply Irradiated. Deals sqrt(# stacks) damage per second. Each stack has a 15% chance to double (increase by 1) per second. Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_IRRADIATECHANCE_FULL:"辐射概率",STAT_IRRADIATECHANCE_LABEL:"RAD",STAT_IRRADIATECHANCE_STACKDESC:"Deals sqrt(# stacks) damage per second. Each stack has a 15% chance to double (increase by 1) per second.",STAT_ISOLATION_DESC:"Percent reduction to the rate at which spreading conditions (Plague, Balloon, Irradiate, etc.) gain stacks over time.",STAT_ISOLATION_FULL:"隔离",STAT_ISOLATION_LABEL:"ISO",STAT_LEAPCHANCE_DESC:"Chance to gain Leap stacks on attack. Leap stacks are consumed to negate incoming debuff applications (1 stack per debuff stack negated). Values over 100% allow for multiple applications per hit.",STAT_LEAPCHANCE_FULL:"跳跃概率",STAT_LEAPCHANCE_LABEL:"LEP",STAT_LEAPCHANCE_STACKDESC:"Leap stacks are consumed to negate incoming debuff applications (1 stack per debuff stack negated).",STAT_LIFESTEAL_DESC:"将造成的最终伤害按百分比转化为生命值。在所有伤害修正后应用。",STAT_LIFESTEAL_FULL:"生命偷取",STAT_LIFESTEAL_LABEL:"吸血",STAT_MAXDAMAGE_DESC:"伤害波动的上限。基础值为 125%。较高的值可增加峰值伤害潜力。",STAT_MAXDAMAGE_FULL:"最大伤害",STAT_MAXDAMAGE